{"type": "article", "id": 34554, "title": "调料罐有卫生隐患？试试自动开阖的｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-16T23:31:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 25154, "name": "Torafu Architects"}, {"id": 34937, "name": "源源钢艺"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 72, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161116182935XHSpmIZ07U5aFVBh.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Dōzo by Torafu Architects</h3><p>日本的 <a href=\"http://torafu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Torafu 建筑设计事务所</a>最近设计了一套名为 Dōzo 的长凳，希望通过对凳腿的趣味改造，在帮助年长者站起和坐下的同时，吸引路人就坐、促进人们在城市中的互动。每一张长凳都配备了一个作为凳腿一部分的拐杖，共有三种不同的把手造型。座面的边缘采用了斜角设计，整个外形看上去简洁而流畅。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161832247bsvSgVL8QzpfCrc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161832243RCiMEBlIzJDg2Zq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183225JludX3KVMUPDH9Nm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751834\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183224lgkb2sP9QpzGqULS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183225K9fsLlXV5RZGApSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.376111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>GearEye by GearEye</h3><p>设计师 Roie Galitz 是一名摄影爱好者，他在出行前总要反复检查是不是带全了镜头，最近他和设计团队研发了一款方便人们确认物品是否已经带上的智能产品 GearEye。它由一台电子狗和一系列贴在设备上的标签组成，通过配套的应用就能在手机上查看是否带上了物品。自带的定位功能会在物品和用户之间的距离超过 50 厘米之后发出提醒，不用再担心丢三落四找不到东西了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/874608327/geareye-the-ultimate-gear-management-system\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183131uJZ4AWnjpyP3CFIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605882\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161831311OtmjBAQYLK2cqyh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.576606\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183131Tx6leUkdgVNPODqQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.139706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>One Shake by yuansteel</h3><p>台湾设计团队源源钢艺发现餐桌上常见的调味罐设计并不是十全十美：开放式虽然方便拿取但会导致脏东西黏附在洞孔上，密闭式有卫生保障却失去了便利性。为了解决这些问题，源源钢艺设计了这款名为 One Shake 的调味罐。罐盖边缘采用了 360 度的出料设计，每个角度都可以倾倒出调料。特殊结构的盖子会在倾斜角度低于水平约 25 度时自动开启，水平位置时再自动关上，杜绝调料被异物污染，让调味这个动作也变得优雅起来。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/oneshake\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为新台币 1080 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183110km4dbUPhw9foyJTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161831104n8gOWvlC2NKXrms.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183110JxkvZFfj4wHKECuT.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666364\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183113zewSXqcR5J9dtnsZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111618311014MPafRpCelUx3TZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Onddo by Iratzoki Lizaso</h3><p>第一眼看到这盏像是蘑菇一样的台灯时，你觉得它是用什么做的？<a href=\"http://iratzoki-lizaso.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Iratzoki Lizaso</a> 工作室打造的 <a href=\"http://iratzoki-lizaso.com/work/onddo/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Onddo</a> 实际上都是在瓷窑内烧制而成的，设计师们希望将传统工艺与现代的 LED 灯融合在一起，营造出特别的照明效果。根据瓷釉的颜色，这盏台灯也可以变成一盏气氛灯，带给人一种通透的感觉。底座还能用来收纳一些小物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183049XZOPtiL8movqgy1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183049mMa2lQH0fFisz8Xt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161830495XP6tSfIQnVZx8ks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183049haNb4RFUCunD0G3Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.055000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183049dhlkS3fwrx6ZYQMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.804000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plus Minus Zero by Steve Bae</h3><p>在观看了有关人工智能（AI）的电影《her》之后，韩国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/stevebae\" rel=\"nofollow\">Steve Bae</a> 借鉴了无印良品的风格，带来了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43976197/Ai-concept-for-Plus-Minus-Zero\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plus Minus Zero</a> 的 AI 概念设计。人与人之间借助杯子对话的互动方式给予了 Bae 启发，希望通过这种生活中常见物品的造型让 AI 能够更贴近用户的生活。 开关、蓝牙键和控制音量的旋钮都被设计在顶部，外形上也延续了极简的风格。为了方便用户随身携带设备，Bae 还设计了一个皮革制的杯套和配套的吊绳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161830229lxYMTmWhIFzjQDn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183022wPdjcR4QSlpYBrZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183024CIiDXRuzgNBQwhKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183022Cq5JAb2WelaStHyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183023RViM9S7aUAuQWgPF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116183023AfOZF5rY4woaPkpu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.687143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>OSTRICH PILLOW GO by StudioBananaThings</h3><p>长途旅行时，人们往往会带上 U 形颈枕为头颈提供支撑，最近来自英国的 <a href=\"http://www.studiobananathings.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">StudioBananaThings</a> 带来了一款能够无死角地包裹住颈部的颈枕 <a href=\"https://ostrichpillow.com/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">OSTRICH PILLOW GO</a>。它采用记忆海绵制成，使用时通过藏在两端内部的磁铁吸附在一起。卷起后它的大小会缩减 60%，方便用户携带。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ostrich-pillow/ostrich-pillow-go-maximum-comfort-sleep-for-all-ne\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 35 英镑。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116233948Wm2ZbjTHM3PYsGXq.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.626667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116233941R5uqlfHTgW9pAOEZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.626667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116233941roHLhFIKpOnybwVB.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.623529\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116233941nzUpRlytNBJDV0wF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732353\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}